Create src/components/TaskViewModal/TaskViewModal.tsx

This component is a modal overlay that opens when the user
clicks "View" on any task row in ScheduledTask.tsx.
It shows task details in READ-ONLY view mode.
A separate prompt (Modal Prompt 2) adds edit mode.

The existing Sidebar.tsx, Header.tsx, and AppLayout.tsx
